      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities performed on geometry, flow regime, and fluid conditions representative of the CPB COU.",
      "rationale": "Validation uses the FDA generic centrifugal pump, which shares impeller geometry class and Reynolds number range with the target CPB device. Blood analog fluid properties are matched. The validation scenario is judged highly relevant to the COU."
