    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors have been assessed and meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 3. The equivalency of input parameters factor was not formally assessed; the team judged that the geometric similarity between the FDA generic pump and the target CPB device is sufficient to support the decision without a formal equivalency analysis. The overall credibility evidence is considered adequate to accept the CFD hemolysis predictions for the CPB COU decision.",
